title: Ep 26 - Living Up To Our Potential
itunes:title: Ep 26 - Living Up To Our Potential
description:
How often do we really live up to our true potential? I mean 100% true potential. It is usually not as much as we should. We are more powerful than we give ourselves credit for and in this episode we talk about how to live up to our true potential and speak about what our lives could be like if we did.
